{"tid":1895300,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實「無間道」個結局都幾反映到警隊現實","createTime":"2020-02-24T12:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T15:15:55.000Z","uid":8968,"like":60,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a96d0d2841e77eff1044f36e1ac4c537a9bc282f","tid":1895300,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:40:28.000Z","msg":"真係為左申張正義既（朝偉）就忍辱負重做臥底 最後都係要死<br />\n為左錢利益既毅進仔（劉華狗）就入去勾結黑社會一步步爬上去<br />\n最後仲唔洗死<br />\n因為警隊入面根本就係好多（林家棟）<br />\n冇撚腦 只顧利益既散狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221feb66d8b3daf00f95ed8417e1c5cd2d831917","tid":1895300,"uid":241543,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:46:22.000Z","msg":"noted with thanks"},{"pid":"a812f232439302a4779438a6beeab7caa171e5cf","tid":1895300,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:48:40.000Z","msg":"H_LXXXX = 林家棟"},{"pid":"d67e65e506d8a1bffea5e6d6d13923e5e2713888","tid":1895300,"uid":52313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:51:15.000Z","msg":"How about 傻強？"},{"pid":"520f176899fd2185f8f515bdc62fababfa50591c","tid":1895300,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"221feb66d8b3daf00f95ed8417e1c5cd2d831917","tid":1895300,"uid":241543,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:46:22.000Z","msg":"noted with thanks"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食屎仔"},{"pid":"bb85d7cd3111716cad62e7b8002f470fddccecf1","tid":1895300,"uid":241543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"520f176899fd2185f8f515bdc62fababfa50591c","tid":1895300,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"221feb66d8b3daf00f95ed8417e1c5cd2d831917","tid":1895300,"uid":241543,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2